---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---
<section class="relative overflow-hidden group/hero min-h-[80vh] flex items-center">

  <Image
    src="/hero.jpg"
    alt="Fachada del Sanatorio San José"
    width={1920}
    height={1080}
    loading="eager" 
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-[10000ms] ease-out scale-105 group-hover/hero:scale-100"
  />

  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-950/90 via-slate-950/70 to-slate-950/50 md:bg-gradient-to-r md:from-slate-950/80 md:via-slate-950/60 md:to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-44 w-full z-10">

    <div
      class="max-w-3xl text-white"
      data-aos="fade-up"
      data-aos-duration="1000"
    >

      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-[1.2] md:leading-[1.1] mb-6 tracking-tight bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-white to-slate-200">
        Desde mediados del siglo XX, el Sanatorio San José acompaña de forma ininterrumpida a la comunidad de Villa Elisa y su zona de influencia.
      </h2>

      <p class="text-base md:text-xl text-slate-250/90 leading-relaxed mb-8 md:mb-10 max-w-2xl">
        Brindamos atención integral con profesionales especializados, diagnóstico y guardia permanente.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">

        <a
          href="https://sistemas.sanjoseve.com.ar/Turnos/"
          class="bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 text-white px-8 py-3.5 md:py-4 rounded-2xl font-semibold text-center transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/20 hover:shadow-blue-700/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5 active:translate-y-0 text-sm md:text-base"
        >
          Solicitar turno
        </a>

        <a
          href="contacto"
          class="bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 px-8 py-3.5 md:py-4 rounded-2xl font-semibold text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 active:translate-y-0 text-sm md:text-base"
        >
          Contacto
        </a>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>